{"tid":1301920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老思想-奴隸化既儒家思想","createTime":"2019-07-09T18:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T18:56:02.000Z","uid":116198,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b4e57bed7dceea5ae13dc043ca7fe4a089892f76","tid":1301920,"uid":116198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:35:44.000Z","msg":"廢老覺得香港係佢地建設，交稅俾後生讀書、<br />\n後生享受社會公共服務，應該要好好感激廢老，<br />\n正正中國人思想，欠吓既人情 要十倍報恩、養之恩情大過天，<br />\n<br />\n另外，中國人信奉明清時期儒家思想，君尊臣卑、父權子孝、愚忠，就算上位者出錯，亦要跟隨，而且強調臣卑子孝實行，無視上階應有付出。<br />\n<br />\n現今香港社會，中西文化合璧，廢老一路享受父權上層既權利，但義務責任就實行西方平等既一套。<br />\n依種情況就好似腐敗既貴族，貪戀權利，逃避責任。<br />\n<br />\n希望各位平時遇到冷眼旁觀既廢老鬧後生仔，可以無視佢地，佢地只係一班利己主義者，企係有利益既環境去批判唔聽佢地話既後生仔。利己既人，係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚自私</span></span>，點會聽人講野。"},{"pid":"8101c59e70b034566c927b91f3389a9016548aba","tid":1301920,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>7.10</strong> - <ins>TVB港姐</ins> - <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1300556\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/1300556</a><br />\n<strong>7.10</strong> - <ins>麥小姐追思會</ins> ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場 - 19:00~22:30<br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>梁烈士公眾告別禮</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=72dfe45e\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>油尖旺區議會夢遊</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_d